                        <hr>
                        <li>
                            <h3><b>Introduction-</b></h3>
                        </li>
                        <p><b>Skills</b> are the building blocks of personal and professional growth.
                            <mark>They represent the abilities we develop through learning, practice, and
                                experience.</mark>
                            In today’s fast-changing world, knowledge alone is not enough — it is the application of
                            that knowledge through skills that creates opportunities. Whether technical or soft, skills
                            shape how we work, communicate, and innovate. The <b>future</b> belongs to those who
                            continuously learn and adapt their skills to meet new challenges.
                        </p>
                        
                              
                        <center>
                            <figure>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <img src="skills.jpeg" alt="skills" width="600" height="200">
                                    <figcaption>skills development</figcaption>
                                </figcaption>
                            </figure>
                        </center>
                        <hr>
                        <li>
                            <h3><strong>Why Skills Matter?</strong></h3>
                        </li>
                        <p>Skills matter because they transform knowledge into action and potential into results. They
                            enable individuals to solve problems, communicate effectively, and adapt to changing
                            environments.
                            <mark>In today’s competitive world, skills are not just an advantage — they are a necessity
                                for growth and success.</mark> From technical expertise to creativity and teamwork,
                            skills empower people to achieve goals, unlock opportunities, and shape a better future.
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Turn knowledge into real-life application</li>
                            <li>Improve communication and collaboration</li>
                            <li>Build confidence and self-reliance</li>
                            <li>Open doors to career opportunities</li>
                            <li>Develop problem-solving and adaptability</li>
                            <li>Drive innovation and future growth</li>
                        </ul>
                        </ul>
                        <video controls width="800" height="200" poster="poster.png">
                            <source src="2516160-hd_1920_1080_24fps.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                            Your browser does not support the video tag.
                        </video>
                        <hr>
                        <li>
                            <h3><strong>Courses: The Gateway to Knowledge-</strong></h3>
                          
                        </li>
                        
                        <p>Courses act as a gateway to knowledge, offering structured learning that helps individuals
                            gain both theoretical understanding and practical expertise. They provide a clear path for
                            developing skills, exploring new areas of interest, and staying updated with the latest
                            advancements. In today’s world, where continuous learning is essential, courses not only
                            expand knowledge but also open doors to new opportunities. By enrolling in courses, learners
                            invest in their growth, strengthen their abilities, and prepare themselves for future
                            challenges.</p>
                        <center>
                            <table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="10">
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Course Type</th>
                                    <th>Purpose/Focus</th>
                                    <th>Example Platforms</th>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Technical Courses</td>
                                    <td>Build coding, IT, and software skills</td>
                                    <td>Coursera, Udemy, edX</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Professional Skills</td>
                                    <td>Improve communication, leadership, management</td>
                                    <td>LinkedIn Learning, Skillshare</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Creative Courses</td>
                                    <td>Enhance design, art, music, or writing</td>
                                    <td>Domestika, Skillshare</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Business Courses</td>
                                    <td>Learn entrepreneurship, marketing, finance</td>
                                    <td>Coursera, HubSpot Academy</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Soft Skills</td>
                                    <td>Develop teamwork, adaptability, problem-solving</td>
                                    <td>Udemy, FutureLearn</td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </center>
                        <li>
                            <hr>
                            <h3><strong>Useful Links & Resources-</strong></h3>
                        </li>
                        
                        <p>Useful links and resources act as a bridge between learning and growth. They provide easy
                            access to trusted platforms, reference materials, and communities that support continuous
                            skill development. With the right resources, learners can explore new courses, stay updated
                            with the latest industry trends, and connect with opportunities that help them achieve both
                            personal and professional goals. Some of the most popular platforms include:</p>
